column4: Three lanes outbound and one lane inbound from 10:30 pm to 12:30 am.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: All traffic from the stadium must turn right onto Tates Creek Rd.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: Outbound Tates Creek traffic from Cooper Dr must turn left to Alumni Dr.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: Inbound left turn lane to Alumni Dr is closed.
Cooper Dr is one way from the stadium to Tates Creek Rd.
